{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_013bXSZoLU8ecPq5DDoybDQd","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01MB7g9KKuJLn5A2jdXfYQEk","name":"StructuredOutput","input":{"id":"web-application-01_DbAccessSpec_Example--s16","title":"オブジェクトのフィールドの値の登録機能(Mapのサブクラス編)","no_knowledge_content":false,"official_doc_urls":[],"index":[{"id":"s1","title":"オブジェクトのフィールドの値の登録機能(Mapのサブクラス編)","hints":["ParameterizedSqlPStatement","executeUpdateByMap","addBatchMap","executeBatch","getBatchSize","Map更新","バッチ更新","一括更新","BATCH_EXECUTE_MAX_CNT"]}],"sections":{"s1":"## 1件のデータを更新する場合\n\n`ParameterizedSqlPStatement.executeUpdateByMap(Map)` でMapのデータを1件更新する。\n\n```java\nMap<String, Object> sales = new HashMap<String, Object>();\nsales.put(\"CST_ID\", \"00001\");\nsales.put(\"KINGAKU\", \"200\");\n\nParameterizedSqlPStatement statement = getParameterizedSqlStatement(\"UPDATE_SALES\");\nint updCnt = statement.executeUpdateByMap(sales);\n```\n\n## 複数件を更新する場合\n\n複数件を一括で更新する場合の注意点は、:ref:`JDBC標準機能<executeBatch-label>` と同じである。\n\n```java\n// 1回のexecuteBatchで更新する最大の件数\nprivate static final int BATCH_EXECUTE_MAX_CNT = 1000;\n\nParameterizedSqlPStatement statement = getParameterizedSqlStatement(\"UPDATE_SALES\");\n\nfor (Map<String, ?> sales : salesList) {\n    statement.addBatchMap(sales);\n    if (statement.getBatchSize() == BATCH_EXECUTE_MAX_CNT) {\n        statement.executeBatch();\n    }\n}\nif (statement.getBatchSize() != 0) {\n    statement.executeBatch();\n}\n```"}}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":17488,"cache_read_input_tokens":18643,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":17488,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a0df0e86-2f70-405f-86b8-d7f56a3ec612","uuid":"d444b2ce-ba53-47c2-8c09-cf73a7898872"}
